				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok People, to kill the PoD in gfay, get a few lvl 50+ mages and bind them at wizzy spires.  Have them buff their pets as best they can, and send them in from max range.  As soon as you hit the /pet attack button, gate to wizzy spires.  The PoD doesnt attack pets, and just runs around screaming, &quot;You Fool!&quot;  This works if you have enough mage pets.  Necro pets work too.  Just make sure you gate away or he will go after you.  He hits for 350, and complete heals himself.  I believe he has 100% magic resistance, but that is unconfirmed.  If you do this, he will die.  And don't flame this, ive seen it done.
